What generation am I in if I was born on November 22nd 1965?

You are part of Generation X

Like to see more about Generations? Click here to go to our interactive generations table.

Click here to see more about Sagittarius

XI • XXII • MCMLXV

What is 1965-11-22 converted to roman numerals? Above is the date 11-22-1965 converted into roman numerals.

The above date is written in the traditional western/American style of writing dates. Formatted in the order of

Month-Day-Year. If you prefer the European way of writing dates (Which is day-month-year) the roman numerals would be written XXII • XI • MCMLXV.

The above timer is a countdown clock for your next birthday! (Assuming you were born on 1965-11-22) This timer is automatically updated, and is accurate all the way up to the nearest second. Watch as your next birthday ticks closer and closer right before your eyes. If you were born on november-22-1965, your next birthday is only 112 days away.
